      "comment": "HARA'S BARRY (1) is a first starter from the Jemma Daley yard by Tommy Shelby out of Hara's Betty. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Respect any strong moves in the market. NAUTICAL BLUE (5) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 0.8 lengths (20.51) behind Tea Rose at this track. Will give a great sight again. EVANDER (2) is on debut with a good inside draw a bonus. Can kick off with a good run. MY NAMES JEFF (7) is by Bernardo out of Glittering Gaby making debut. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Profiles nicely but market best guide to ability.",
